{"tid":58546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕點火燒流浪漢,德國7難民圖謀殺被捕","createTime":"2016-12-29T02:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T02:33:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd20a68e340684b8f582f590c97019fdbc0c39b6","tid":58546,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:07:57.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=8jSl%2F07Erb5WLRU5GsSSWwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=8bcf6f0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 德國柏林7名難民涉嫌於聖誕節當日，在火車站向一名正在睡覺的流浪漢點火，之後更在旁哈哈大笑。警方隨後發放閉路電視畫面，通緝他們，其中6人向警方自首，第7人被捕，他們全以難民身分到德國尋求庇護，現被控意圖謀殺。 <br />\n<br />\n檢察官表示，7名疑犯年齡介乎15至21歲，6人來自敍利亞，1人來自利比亞。案中的37歲流浪漢，聖誕當日凌晨2時喝醉後，在火車站長椅上睡覺。期間7名難民向流浪漢點火，途人見狀立即將火撲熄，流浪漢未有受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n柏林警方介入調查，並發布閉路電視畫面，7名疑犯容貌清晰可見，他們事後更在列車中嬉笑胡鬧。最終6人向警方自首，第7名疑犯則被警方拘捕。 <br />\n<br />\n[url=<a href=\"https://postimg.org/image/lv2qyevvl/]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.org%2Fimage%2Flv2qyevvl%2F%5D&d=8jSl%2F07Erb5WLRU5GsSSWwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=cfe9a78b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://postimg.org/image/lv2qyevvl/]</a><img src=\"https://s24.postimg.org/mxcxgyep1/01_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs24.postimg.org%2Fmxcxgyep1%2F01_02b.jpg&h=4f5c2a92&s={SIZE}\" />[/url] <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161228/bknint-20161228104643023-1228_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161228%2Fbknint-20161228104643023-1228_17011_001.html&d=8jSl%2F07Erb5WLRU5GsSSWwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=a6703185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161228/bknint-20161228104643023-1228_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3b4a30369716abba84a133dba6ad30472d335a49","tid":58546,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:10:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: 